snippet.title: Beauty and the Beast: The Story of Boston Rob & Amber - Survivor: All-Stars
snippet.description:
Boston Rob Mariano & Ambuh Brkich, they infamously crushed everyone on Survivor: All-Stars and what was left behind in their wake? An unexpected love story of a Robfather and his girlfriend that ends with the proposal of a lifetime at the Survivor finale.

What are the benefits to joining the Patreon for you?
1. You get all of the videos I upload weeks early.
2. You get to pick who I make story videos about. (Survivor, The Amazing Race, Big Brother, etc.)
3. A new Patreon only exclusive video each month.
4. All podcasts are downloadable as MP3's 
5. Your financial support helps the channel to continue and increase the quality and quantity of the videos.
Join today! - https://www.patreon.com/onceuponanislandchannel

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/onceuponanislandchannel
Twitter - https://twitter.com/upon_island
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/once_upon_an_island_channel/
Email  - ouaichannel@gmail.com
Website - http://www.woodenfilms.com/

00:00 - Introduction
12:17 - Rising Action
33:03 - Rising Action: Part Two

01:09:13 - Final Tribal Council
01:18:13 - Resolution
